    "body": "> The problem is that when you have large damage that spread damage produces a staircase instead of a continuous-ish decay.\r\n\r\nBut in terms of actual effect on balance, going 70-30-10 is no different to 7-3-1. Is that really such a problem?\r\nAnd if this is only about the shipping mods, we could simply take the Falloff approach on all weapons, thanks to inheritance that would now be easier than changing all base damages directly anyway.\r\n\r\n> Is there a way to have the unit do 1 damage every other shot if its below the %?\r\n\r\nI suspect that the coding required for this would be too complicated to chose this over possible alternatives."
