    "body": "After the green light for the changes and all the progression made in the PR for the RA mod, I started to do the same changes for the TD mod. Luckily, it seems less time consuming than the RA mod. Thanks to fewer custom weapon rules in missions.\r\n\r\nI'll start with the D2K mod after the TD mod. This could also be changed relatively fast. The values of D2K will be multiplied by 10, bringing it in line with the other mods. I presume this is also wanted (looking at @MustaphaTR, as our main contributor for D2K, for conformation).\r\n\r\nI'll have this done well in time before Christmas.\r\n\r\nLast but not least is the TS mod. I'll do it after all the PRs are finished."
